00:00:09.109 --> 00:00:11.211 position:10% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>We are now in the last</i>
 <i>minutes of the match.</i>

00:00:11.245 --> 00:00:14.181 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>And Team Musashi is</i>
 <i>winning by a single goal.</i>

00:00:14.214 --> 00:00:15.783 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Can Team Nankatsu</i>
 <i>tie the match</i>

00:00:15.817 --> 00:00:17.519 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>before the second half</i>
 <i>is over?</i>

00:00:17.552 --> 00:00:19.754 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>You can cut the tension</i>
 <i>with a knife.</i>

00:00:19.787 --> 00:00:21.088 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>The prince, Jun Misugi,</i>

00:00:21.121 --> 00:00:23.090 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>is holding himself</i>
 <i>up against the goalpost.</i>

00:00:23.123 --> 00:00:26.126 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>He's not leaving anything</i>
 <i>up to chance.</i>

00:00:26.159 --> 00:00:27.461 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>With two minutes</i>
 <i>on the clock,</i>

00:00:27.494 --> 00:00:30.130 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>no one knows what</i>
 <i>exactly will happen.</i>

00:02:14.468 --> 00:02:15.870 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[whistle]
-[narr] <i>Episode 22:</i>

00:02:15.903 --> 00:02:16.804 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>Additional Time of Destiny.</i>

00:02:16.838 --> 00:02:17.905 position:21% line:83% align:start
You're going to lose,
Musashi.

00:02:17.939 --> 00:02:19.707 position:47% line:83% align:start
Ha!
That was a good one.

00:02:19.741 --> 00:02:21.643 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Team Nankatsu</i>
 <i>switches to offense.</i>

00:02:21.676 --> 00:02:23.044 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>They're trying to find</i>
 <i>an opening</i>

00:02:23.077 --> 00:02:24.545 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>to squeeze through</i>
 <i>the airtight defense</i>

00:02:24.579 --> 00:02:25.546 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>from Musashi,</i>

00:02:25.580 --> 00:02:27.715 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>but they don't plan on</i>
 <i>letting them pass.</i>

00:02:27.749 --> 00:02:29.817 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>They're counting on</i>
 <i>keeping the scoreboard as is</i>

00:02:29.851 --> 00:02:31.184 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>no matter what happens.</i>

00:02:31.218 --> 00:02:32.386 position:24% line:89% align:start
Minoru and Shinji,

00:02:32.419 --> 00:02:34.856 position:16% line:83% align:start
I want you both to cover
Tsubasa no matter what.

00:02:34.889 --> 00:02:36.090 position:41% line:83% align:start
-[gasp]
-Team Nankatsu

00:02:36.124 --> 00:02:38.392 position:16% line:83% align:start
depends solely on Tsubasa
to score their goals.

00:02:38.425 --> 00:02:39.694 position:19% line:89% align:start
Forget about the ball.

00:02:39.727 --> 00:02:42.730 position:10% line:83% align:start
I want you to cover Tsubasa.
Don't lose sight of him.

00:02:42.764 --> 00:02:43.064 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

00:02:43.097 --> 00:02:44.098 position:38% line:89% align:start
What? No!

00:02:44.132 --> 00:02:45.499 position:19% line:83% align:start
Hey, what's wrong with
all of you?

00:02:45.533 --> 00:02:47.267 position:27% line:83% align:start
It's obvious that
they'd cover Tsubasa.

00:02:47.300 --> 00:02:48.970 position:27% line:83% align:start
What'd you think
would happen?

00:02:49.003 --> 00:02:50.772 position:30% line:83% align:start
Our team isn't
just about him.

00:02:50.805 --> 00:02:51.639 position:21% line:89% align:start
It's about all of us.

00:02:51.673 --> 00:02:53.641 position:35% line:83% align:start
Nankatsu is
an eleven man team.

00:02:53.675 --> 00:02:54.709 position:24% line:89% align:start
This is our moment.

00:02:54.742 --> 00:02:57.377 position:21% line:83% align:start
Show them what makes
Nankatsu an incredible team.

00:02:57.411 --> 00:02:58.813 position:19% line:89% align:start
You're right, Captain.

00:02:58.846 --> 00:02:59.947 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Mhm.
-Of course.

00:02:59.981 --> 00:03:02.884 position:16% line:83% align:start
Now you'll see first hand
Shutetsu's quartet's power.

00:03:02.917 --> 00:03:03.951 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

00:03:03.985 --> 00:03:06.988 position:30% line:83% align:start
Akira, Hiroshi,
cover them two now.

00:03:07.021 --> 00:03:08.122 position:44% line:89% align:start
What?

00:03:08.156 --> 00:03:09.389 position:44% line:83% align:start
Uh...
They're not open.

00:03:09.423 --> 00:03:11.559 position:13% line:83% align:start
Listen up, he's planning on
passing right.

00:03:11.592 --> 00:03:13.628 position:19% line:83% align:start
-Kazuya get on him now.
-Yeah!

00:03:13.661 --> 00:03:14.595 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:03:14.629 --> 00:03:16.597 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>And Musashi</i>
 <i>strangles the offense.</i>

00:03:16.631 --> 00:03:18.265 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>Number 9 can't seem</i>
 <i>to pass the ball.</i>

00:03:18.298 --> 00:03:19.534 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
 <i>This can't be happening.</i>

00:03:19.567 --> 00:03:22.603 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Misugi is anticipating</i>
 <i>all of our movements.</i>

00:03:22.637 --> 00:03:23.738 position:38% line:89% align:start
[chuckle]

00:03:23.771 --> 00:03:26.306 position:16% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>It's as if we were</i>
 <i>spectating a chess match.</i>

00:03:26.339 --> 00:03:27.775 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>Prince Misugi</i>
 <i>is moving his pieces</i>

00:03:27.809 --> 00:03:31.344 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>as if he were a computer,</i>
 <i>managing a perfect defense.</i>

00:03:31.378 --> 00:03:34.115 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Fukuyama] <i>Good.</i>
 <i>This match is ours now.</i>

00:03:34.148 --> 00:03:35.883 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Team Nankatsu</i>
 <i>is in a bind.</i>

00:03:35.917 --> 00:03:38.318 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>They have no way to</i>
 <i>close the gap with the goal</i>

00:03:38.351 --> 00:03:40.420 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>and time's still</i>
 <i>ticking away.</i>

00:03:40.454 --> 00:03:41.622 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>There's less than</i>
 <i>one minute.</i>

00:03:41.656 --> 00:03:43.691 position:21% line:83% align:start
Nankatsu already lost
their momentum.

00:03:43.725 --> 00:03:46.194 position:21% line:83% align:start
Listen up, go and get
the ball from them.

00:03:46.226 --> 00:03:47.695 position:33% line:83% align:start
If we manage
to get it back now,

00:03:47.729 --> 00:03:49.764 position:16% line:83% align:start
they won't have any means
of attacking.

00:03:49.797 --> 00:03:50.397 position:33% line:89% align:start
Yes, Captain!

00:03:51.231 --> 00:03:52.432 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Now Musashi</i>
 <i>is the one's</i>

00:03:52.466 --> 00:03:53.835 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>pressuring Nankatsu</i>
 <i>to get the ball.</i>

00:03:53.868 --> 00:03:55.570 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>But Team Nankatsu</i>
 <i>is doing their best</i>

00:03:55.603 --> 00:03:57.437 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>to keep control of it on</i>
 <i>their side, no matter what.</i>

00:03:57.471 --> 00:03:59.272 position:21% line:83% align:start
This can't happen...
The match is gonna be over.

00:03:59.306 --> 00:04:00.141 position:19% line:89% align:start
We got to do something.

00:04:00.174 --> 00:04:01.943 position:35% line:83% align:start
-It's mine.
-[gasp]

00:04:01.976 --> 00:04:03.177 position:16% line:83% align:start
-[ann] <i>What's happening?</i>
-Whoa!

00:04:03.211 --> 00:04:05.880 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>Nankatsu gets distracted</i>
 <i>and loses the ball.</i>

00:04:05.913 --> 00:04:07.347 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>Now Team Musashi has it.</i>

00:04:07.380 --> 00:04:08.750 position:21% line:89% align:start
Team Musashi my foot.

00:04:08.783 --> 00:04:09.517 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:04:09.550 --> 00:04:10.852 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ann]
 <i>But Ryo Ishizaki appears</i>

00:04:10.885 --> 00:04:12.987 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>and gets the ball back</i>
 <i>with a great slide tackle.</i>

00:04:13.020 --> 00:04:14.989 position:33% line:83% align:start
You go, Ryo.
What a great job!

00:04:15.022 --> 00:04:16.323 position:13% line:89% align:start
Everybody, run to the goal.

00:04:17.457 --> 00:04:19.292 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>It looks like</i>
 <i>this will be the last play</i>

00:04:19.326 --> 00:04:20.661 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>from Nankatsu.</i>

00:04:20.695 --> 00:04:22.830 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>But Tsubasa</i>
 <i>is totally covered</i>

00:04:22.864 --> 00:04:24.632 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>and he can't even move.</i>

00:04:25.398 --> 00:04:26.734 position:30% line:89% align:start
You can do it.

00:04:26.768 --> 00:04:27.802 position:21% line:89% align:start
There's no time left.

00:04:28.836 --> 00:04:32.173 position:33% line:83% align:start
Why don't you
stop covering my Tsubasa?

00:04:32.206 --> 00:04:33.908 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Hajime Taki</i>
 <i>is ready to shoot and...</i>

00:04:33.941 --> 00:04:35.943 position:35% line:89% align:start
[growling]

00:04:35.977 --> 00:04:36.744 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[grunt]
-[ann] <i>He can't shoot</i>

00:04:36.778 --> 00:04:38.780 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>and passes it</i>
 <i>to Taro Misaki.</i>

00:04:38.813 --> 00:04:39.714 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>He looks very worried.</i>

00:04:39.747 --> 00:04:41.849 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Taro] <i>No, this can't be</i>
 <i>the end of us.</i>

00:04:43.350 --> 00:04:44.719 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>We made a promise to get to</i>

00:04:44.752 --> 00:04:46.020 position:19% line:83% align:start
- <i>the finals together,</i>
-[gasp]

00:04:46.053 --> 00:04:47.555 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>and I'm going to keep it!</i>

00:04:47.588 --> 00:04:48.890 position:19% line:89% align:start
What's he trying to do?

00:04:48.923 --> 00:04:51.324 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Team Nankatsu</i>
 <i>hasn't thrown in towel yet,</i>

00:04:51.358 --> 00:04:52.627 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>and Taro Misaki is running</i>

00:04:52.660 --> 00:04:54.228 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>with great speed</i>
 <i>to the goal.</i>

00:04:54.262 --> 00:04:56.264 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>Will he try and</i>
 <i>challenge Misugi?</i>

00:04:56.296 --> 00:04:58.331 position:35% line:83% align:start
Listen up,
don't you let Misaki

00:04:58.365 --> 00:05:00.001 position:27% line:83% align:start
get anywhere near
the danger zone.

00:05:00.034 --> 00:05:01.269 position:24% line:83% align:start
Go and get the ball
from him.

00:05:01.301 --> 00:05:02.603 position:19% line:89% align:start
We can't let him shoot.

00:05:02.637 --> 00:05:04.272 position:19% line:83% align:start
We won't let him shoot,
Captain.

00:05:04.304 --> 00:05:05.773 position:38% line:83% align:start
You won't
get through us so easily.

00:05:05.807 --> 00:05:08.341 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>No chance. Even if I got</i>
 <i>their attention,</i>

00:05:08.375 --> 00:05:11.245 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>they haven't stopped</i>
 <i>covering Tsubasa.</i>

00:05:11.279 --> 00:05:13.346 position:41% line:83% align:start
[pants]
 <i>What can I do?</i>

00:05:13.380 --> 00:05:15.415 position:44% line:83% align:start
Taro!
What're you thinking about?

00:05:15.448 --> 00:05:16.751 position:30% line:89% align:start
Shoot the ball.

00:05:16.784 --> 00:05:17.985 position:41% line:89% align:start
Genzo.

00:05:18.019 --> 00:05:19.120 position:21% line:89% align:start
You can do it, Taro.

00:05:19.153 --> 00:05:20.988 position:13% line:89% align:start
Forget about me and shoot.

00:05:21.022 --> 00:05:23.925 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Kick the ball.
-[panting]

00:05:23.958 --> 00:05:25.693 position:16% line:89% align:start
Okay, it's now or never.

00:05:25.726 --> 00:05:26.694 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:05:26.727 --> 00:05:29.063 position:16% line:83% align:start
He won't kick to the left
with me being here.

00:05:29.096 --> 00:05:30.798 position:30% line:83% align:start
Tatsuya you go
and get the right.

00:05:30.832 --> 00:05:31.232 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yes!

00:05:31.265 --> 00:05:32.499 position:41% line:89% align:start
[reac]

00:05:32.533 --> 00:05:34.168 position:16% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Taro Misaki shoots</i>
 <i>with all of his strength</i>

00:05:34.202 --> 00:05:35.269 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>to the left side</i>
 <i>of the goal.</i>

00:05:35.303 --> 00:05:36.804 position:41% line:89% align:start
[yell]

00:05:36.838 --> 00:05:39.774 position:30% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Um, uh...</i>
 <i>But the goalie deflects it!</i>

00:05:39.807 --> 00:05:41.075 position:19% line:83% align:start
- <i>Will this be the end</i>
-[gasps]

00:05:41.108 --> 00:05:42.710 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>for team Nankatsu?</i>

00:05:42.743 --> 00:05:43.711 position:27% line:89% align:start
Not yet it won't!

00:05:43.744 --> 00:05:46.080 position:21% line:83% align:start
The match isn't over
until it's over.

00:05:46.113 --> 00:05:47.181 position:33% line:83% align:start
I'm going to
keep on playing

00:05:47.215 --> 00:05:49.784 position:19% line:83% align:start
and I'll give it my all
until the end.

00:05:49.817 --> 00:05:50.785 position:38% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa!

00:05:51.786 --> 00:05:53.721 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Tsubasa gets</i>
 <i>the ball back.</i>

00:05:53.754 --> 00:05:54.555 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>Nankatsu has</i>

00:05:54.589 --> 00:05:55.790 position:19% line:83% align:start
- <i>one last opportunity.</i>
-[gasp]

00:05:55.823 --> 00:05:57.992 position:16% line:83% align:start
Tsubasa could definitely
score from that distance.

00:05:58.025 --> 00:06:00.393 position:21% line:83% align:start
Don't let him shoot.
You have to stop him!

00:06:00.427 --> 00:06:02.096 position:19% line:83% align:start
If you cover him well,
he won't have a way.

00:06:02.129 --> 00:06:02.763 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Yeah.
-Yeah.

00:06:02.797 --> 00:06:03.798 position:47% line:89% align:start
No.

00:06:03.831 --> 00:06:06.667 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Incredible,</i>
 <i>Tsubasa is totally covered</i>

00:06:06.701 --> 00:06:08.401 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>with four players</i>
 <i>surrounding him.</i>

00:06:08.435 --> 00:06:11.839 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>It's impossible for him</i>
 <i>to try to shoot the ball.</i>

00:06:11.873 --> 00:06:13.808 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>The referee</i>
 <i>looks at his watch.</i>

00:06:13.841 --> 00:06:14.809 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:06:14.842 --> 00:06:15.543 position:38% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa!

00:06:15.576 --> 00:06:16.711 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Tsubasa!
-Tsubasa!

00:06:16.744 --> 00:06:17.712 position:38% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa!

00:06:17.745 --> 00:06:20.848 position:16% line:83% align:start
What're you waiting for?
Get the ball from him.

00:06:20.882 --> 00:06:21.082 position:38% line:89% align:start
 <i>I can't.</i>

00:06:22.216 --> 00:06:24.352 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>I can't give up now.</i>
 <i>Especially now.</i>

00:06:24.417 --> 00:06:26.153 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>There has to be a way.</i>

00:06:27.054 --> 00:06:28.723 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>There must be a way.</i>

00:06:28.756 --> 00:06:29.924 position:38% line:89% align:start
 <i>But how?</i>

00:06:29.957 --> 00:06:30.958 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:06:31.859 --> 00:06:32.927 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:06:32.960 --> 00:06:36.130 position:13% line:83% align:start
I know how to break through
your defense, Musashi.

00:06:36.163 --> 00:06:37.632 position:35% line:89% align:start
By flying!

00:06:37.665 --> 00:06:38.666 position:27% line:83% align:start
-What's happe--?
-[ann] <i>Wow,</i>

00:06:38.699 --> 00:06:39.834 position:24% line:83% align:start
- <i>Tsubasa wakes up</i>
-What?!

00:06:39.867 --> 00:06:42.937 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>and raises the ball</i>
 <i>high into the sky.</i>

00:06:42.970 --> 00:06:43.571 position:41% line:89% align:start
[yell]

00:06:43.604 --> 00:06:44.672 position:41% line:83% align:start
-[gasp]
-What's he--?

00:06:44.705 --> 00:06:47.008 position:27% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Tsubasa is</i>
 <i>suspended in midair.</i>

00:06:50.645 --> 00:06:52.313 position:41% line:89% align:start
[yell]

00:06:52.346 --> 00:06:53.381 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ann]
 <i>There it is!</i>

00:06:53.413 --> 00:06:54.515 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>Tsubasa flies</i>

00:06:54.548 --> 00:06:56.416 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>and uses his trademark</i>
 <i>overhead kick</i>

00:06:56.449 --> 00:06:57.919 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>as his last resort.</i>

00:06:57.952 --> 00:06:59.854 position:27% line:89% align:start
Tsu... Tsubasa...

00:07:00.621 --> 00:07:02.790 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>You really are incredible.</i>

00:07:02.823 --> 00:07:04.292 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>You got rid of</i>
 <i>my perfect defense.</i>

00:07:04.325 --> 00:07:05.526 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>But even then...</i>

00:07:05.559 --> 00:07:07.595 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>you didn't have a good</i>
 <i>angle to shoot from.</i>

00:07:08.629 --> 00:07:10.497 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>You wasted</i>
 <i>your last opportunity</i>

00:07:10.531 --> 00:07:13.000 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>because the ball is</i>
 <i>now mine.</i>

00:07:13.034 --> 00:07:14.101 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:07:14.135 --> 00:07:15.336 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:07:15.369 --> 00:07:16.537 position:41% line:89% align:start
[grunt]

00:07:17.838 --> 00:07:18.506 position:33% line:89% align:start
What a goal!

00:07:18.539 --> 00:07:19.640 position:21% line:89% align:start
What an amazing goal!

00:07:19.674 --> 00:07:21.275 position:30% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Just when</i>
 <i>we all thought that</i>

00:07:21.309 --> 00:07:22.610 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>Nankatsu would lose,</i>

00:07:22.643 --> 00:07:25.947 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>Taro Misaki appears with</i>
 <i>an amazing diving header.</i>

00:07:25.980 --> 00:07:28.582 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>Team Nankatsu gets to</i>
 <i>tie the scoreboard</i>

00:07:28.616 --> 00:07:30.351 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>at the last</i>
 <i>possible moment.</i>

00:07:30.384 --> 00:07:33.287 position:30% line:89% align:start
Yeah, I did it!

00:07:33.321 --> 00:07:34.755 position:33% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Misaki</i>
 <i>must be really happy</i>

00:07:34.789 --> 00:07:36.557 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>about the goal</i>
 <i>that tied the match.</i>

00:07:36.590 --> 00:07:39.427 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>And surely his team is</i>
 <i>feeling the relief as well.</i>

00:07:39.459 --> 00:07:41.629 position:16% line:89% align:start
Taro, thank you so much.

00:07:41.662 --> 00:07:43.564 position:24% line:83% align:start
I always knew that
you could do it.

00:07:43.597 --> 00:07:46.466 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[laughing]
-Yeah, good job!

00:07:46.499 --> 00:07:47.768 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Mhm.
-Yeah!

00:07:47.802 --> 00:07:48.970 position:35% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa...

00:07:49.003 --> 00:07:49.303 position:35% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa...

00:07:49.337 --> 00:07:50.638 position:38% line:89% align:start
and Taro.

00:07:50.671 --> 00:07:53.975 position:13% line:83% align:start
It was an excellent header.
You were amazing, Taro.

00:07:54.008 --> 00:07:55.543 position:24% line:89% align:start
Yeah, you go team!

00:07:55.576 --> 00:07:57.445 position:44% line:83% align:start
No...
No, damn it.

00:07:57.477 --> 00:07:58.679 position:27% line:83% align:start
We were so close
to winning.

00:07:58.713 --> 00:08:00.681 position:21% line:83% align:start
-It's just not fair.
-[sobbing]

00:08:00.715 --> 00:08:02.416 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>They had me fooled.</i>

00:08:02.450 --> 00:08:05.019 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>Misaki was the key player</i>
 <i>this whole time.</i>

00:08:05.052 --> 00:08:06.787 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>The overhead kick</i>
 <i>that Tsubasa shot</i>

00:08:06.821 --> 00:08:08.856 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>wasn't him</i>
 <i>trying to score...</i>

00:08:08.889 --> 00:08:11.158 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>It was a direct pass</i>
 <i>towards Misaki.</i>

00:08:12.660 --> 00:08:16.397 position:10% line:83% align:start
 <i>In the end, it was my fault</i>
 <i>for not noticing.</i>

00:08:16.430 --> 00:08:17.965 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>I still have a lot to learn.</i>

00:08:18.866 --> 00:08:21.502 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>Soccer is an extraordinary</i>
 <i>sport.</i>

00:08:22.703 --> 00:08:24.772 position:16% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Now that both teams</i>
 <i>have tied the scoreboard,</i>

00:08:24.805 --> 00:08:27.441 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>the referee will resume</i>
 <i>the match once again.</i>

00:08:27.475 --> 00:08:28.576 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>And Musashi will</i>

00:08:28.609 --> 00:08:30.277 position:21% line:83% align:start
- <i>prepare to attack.</i>
-[whistle]

00:08:31.345 --> 00:08:32.680 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:08:32.713 --> 00:08:34.582 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Minoru]
 <i>We have to win this...</i>

00:08:34.615 --> 00:08:36.250 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Hanji]
 <i>...no matter what happens.</i>

00:08:36.283 --> 00:08:37.551 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
 <i>This is our time.</i>

00:08:37.585 --> 00:08:39.920 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>We can't let our tiredness</i>
 <i>get the best of us.</i>

00:08:39.954 --> 00:08:42.289 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>We have to give it</i>
 <i>everything.</i>

00:08:42.323 --> 00:08:43.624 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>Putting our hearts</i>
 <i>on the field,</i>

00:08:43.657 --> 00:08:45.860 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>until the very last second.</i>

00:08:45.893 --> 00:08:46.827 position:38% line:89% align:start
Tsubasa!

00:08:46.861 --> 00:08:47.661 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:08:47.695 --> 00:08:49.096 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ann]
 <i>Tsubasa takes possession</i>

00:08:49.130 --> 00:08:50.498 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>of the ball swiftly.</i>

00:08:50.531 --> 00:08:51.866 position:24% line:89% align:start
You're so awesome.

00:08:51.899 --> 00:08:52.900 position:35% line:89% align:start
Incredible.

00:08:52.933 --> 00:08:55.703 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>This is Misugi's</i>
 <i>last match ever.</i>

00:08:55.736 --> 00:08:57.104 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>And in spite of</i>
 <i>his heart condition,</i>

00:08:57.138 --> 00:08:58.739 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>he plays giving his all.</i>

00:08:58.773 --> 00:09:01.742 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>He is challenging me</i>
 <i>with everything he's got.</i>

00:09:01.776 --> 00:09:03.444 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>You chose me as</i>
 <i>your last opponent,</i>

00:09:03.477 --> 00:09:04.645 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>and that's why...</i>

00:09:04.678 --> 00:09:06.547 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>I won't let you leave you</i>
 <i>with regrets.</i>

00:09:06.580 --> 00:09:07.681 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>I won't disappoint you.</i>

00:09:07.715 --> 00:09:10.985 position:21% line:83% align:start
Captain! Be careful,
he's going to shoot!

00:09:11.018 --> 00:09:11.819 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:09:11.852 --> 00:09:13.020 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>Get closer, Tsubasa.</i>

00:09:13.054 --> 00:09:15.022 position:35% line:83% align:start
 <i>This time,</i>
 <i>I'm going to stop you.</i>

00:09:15.056 --> 00:09:16.991 position:16% line:89% align:start
This is for you, Misugi!

00:09:24.865 --> 00:09:26.634 position:24% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Tsubasa kicks</i>
 <i>a powerful shot</i>

00:09:26.667 --> 00:09:28.803 position:33% line:83% align:start
 <i>from outside</i>
 <i>the goalkeeper's box.</i>

00:09:28.836 --> 00:09:31.172 position:30% line:83% align:start
[Genzo] Go in!
The water is giving the ball

00:09:31.205 --> 00:09:32.640 position:13% line:89% align:start
more strength and velocity.

00:09:32.673 --> 00:09:33.641 position:13% line:89% align:start
If the goalie's not ready,

00:09:33.674 --> 00:09:35.810 position:16% line:83% align:start
-he won't catch the ball.
-[scream]

00:09:35.843 --> 00:09:38.679 position:16% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>Ah! The goalkeeper</i>
 <i>can't stop the shot.</i>

00:09:38.712 --> 00:09:40.981 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>Misugi throws himself and...</i>

00:09:41.882 --> 00:09:43.451 position:38% line:89% align:start
[whistle]

00:09:43.484 --> 00:09:44.985 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>The prince himself</i>

00:09:45.019 --> 00:09:46.620 position:24% line:83% align:start
- <i>couldn't stop it.</i>
-[grunt]

00:09:46.654 --> 00:09:47.721 position:24% line:83% align:start
- <i>Wait, the referee</i>
-Huh?

00:09:47.755 --> 00:09:48.456 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>hasn't called the play.</i>

00:09:48.489 --> 00:09:49.723 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>Was it the goal,</i>

00:09:49.757 --> 00:09:52.126 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>or could it have been</i>
 <i>the end of the match?</i>

00:10:02.403 --> 00:10:05.005 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:10:05.039 --> 00:10:07.241 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:10:09.477 --> 00:10:10.711 position:35% line:89% align:start
[cheering]

00:10:10.744 --> 00:10:13.981 position:16% line:83% align:start
[ann] <i>And that's a goal,</i>
 <i>ladies and gentlemen!</i>

00:10:14.014 --> 00:10:16.617 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>A goal that made it</i>
 <i>by mere seconds!</i>

00:10:16.650 --> 00:10:17.885 position:16% line:83% align:start
- <i>Team Nankatsu makes it</i>
-Yeah!

00:10:17.918 --> 00:10:21.622 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>to the finals just barely,</i>
 <i>with a 5-4 score.</i>

00:10:21.655 --> 00:10:23.592 position:19% line:83% align:start
- <i>It's truly a miracle.</i>
-Yeah!

00:10:23.624 --> 00:10:24.992 position:44% line:83% align:start
[ann]
 <i>Tsubasa never gave up,</i>

00:10:25.025 --> 00:10:26.694 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>and gives his team</i>
 <i>the victory</i>

00:10:26.727 --> 00:10:30.331 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>with an spectacular</i>
 <i>last minute play.</i>

00:10:31.832 --> 00:10:33.367 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
 <i>We won the match...</i>

00:10:34.368 --> 00:10:35.903 position:24% line:89% align:start
Did we really win?

00:10:35.936 --> 00:10:38.939 position:30% line:83% align:start
Well done, man!
You did it, Tsubasa.

00:10:38.973 --> 00:10:41.543 position:35% line:89% align:start
[laughing]

00:10:41.576 --> 00:10:42.511 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasp]

00:10:42.544 --> 00:10:44.011 position:38% line:89% align:start
[panting]

00:10:44.044 --> 00:10:44.979 position:38% line:89% align:start
Captain!

00:10:45.012 --> 00:10:46.981 position:35% line:89% align:start
[groaning]

00:10:47.915 --> 00:10:50.217 position:24% line:83% align:start
Calm down, manager.
I'm doing fine.

00:10:50.251 --> 00:10:50.784 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chuckles]

00:10:50.818 --> 00:10:52.153 position:24% line:89% align:start
Misugi, are you--?

00:10:53.087 --> 00:10:55.823 position:21% line:83% align:start
Tsubasa, I sincerely
congratulate you.

00:10:55.856 --> 00:10:58.159 position:10% line:89% align:start
You beat me fair and square.

00:10:58.192 --> 00:10:59.660 position:16% line:89% align:start
There's no doubt that...

00:10:59.693 --> 00:11:00.928 position:16% line:89% align:start
you're the better player.

00:11:00.961 --> 00:11:02.597 position:27% line:83% align:start
No, I don't think
that's true.

00:11:02.631 --> 00:11:03.931 position:30% line:89% align:start
I'm really not.

00:11:03.964 --> 00:11:06.233 position:24% line:83% align:start
Had it not been for
your heart condition...

00:11:06.267 --> 00:11:09.538 position:10% line:83% align:start
I'm pretty sure you would've
stopped my last shot.

00:11:09.571 --> 00:11:12.806 position:30% line:83% align:start
Team Musashi is
a very strong opponent.

00:11:12.840 --> 00:11:14.742 position:13% line:89% align:start
That means a lot, Tsubasa.

00:11:14.775 --> 00:11:16.777 position:30% line:83% align:start
But in the end,
you were better.

00:11:17.778 --> 00:11:18.979 position:16% line:89% align:start
You're the better player.

00:11:19.013 --> 00:11:21.550 position:21% line:83% align:start
I can retire without
any doubts.

00:11:21.583 --> 00:11:23.350 position:16% line:89% align:start
What do you mean by that?

00:11:23.384 --> 00:11:24.685 position:13% line:89% align:start
I was only allowed to play

00:11:24.718 --> 00:11:26.820 position:24% line:83% align:start
a couple of minutes
every match.

00:11:26.854 --> 00:11:28.989 position:21% line:83% align:start
And ever since I knew
I'd face you...

00:11:29.023 --> 00:11:31.358 position:13% line:83% align:start
I had decided I would play
a whole match.

00:11:32.693 --> 00:11:33.894 position:16% line:89% align:start
I don't care that I lost.

00:11:33.928 --> 00:11:35.796 position:13% line:89% align:start
I'm truly happy leaving...

00:11:35.829 --> 00:11:37.231 position:21% line:83% align:start
with having faced you
and knowing that

00:11:37.264 --> 00:11:38.667 position:27% line:89% align:start
I played my best.

00:11:38.699 --> 00:11:40.801 position:27% line:83% align:start
That's what means
the most to me.

00:11:41.636 --> 00:11:43.237 position:10% line:89% align:start
I'm truly thankful, Tsubasa.

00:11:44.004 --> 00:11:45.806 position:33% line:83% align:start
And you guys,
you're the best.

00:11:45.839 --> 00:11:48.409 position:27% line:83% align:start
-Don't sweat it.
-It was our pleasure.

00:11:48.442 --> 00:11:49.743 position:24% line:89% align:start
And you too, Yayoi.

00:11:49.777 --> 00:11:52.279 position:19% line:83% align:start
I want to thank you too
for everything you've done.

00:11:52.313 --> 00:11:53.113 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:11:53.147 --> 00:11:54.516 position:24% line:89% align:start
I'm pretty sure...

00:11:54.549 --> 00:11:56.283 position:24% line:83% align:start
that without all of
your help...

00:11:56.317 --> 00:11:59.353 position:13% line:83% align:start
I wouldn't have experienced
such a beautiful match.

00:11:59.386 --> 00:12:00.821 position:30% line:89% align:start
Ah... Captain.

00:12:01.722 --> 00:12:04.124 position:24% line:83% align:start
I owe you big time.
I'm in your debt.

00:12:04.158 --> 00:12:06.293 position:16% line:83% align:start
And now, I'd like for you
to help me

00:12:06.327 --> 00:12:07.494 position:13% line:89% align:start
as the manager of the team.

00:12:08.630 --> 00:12:10.998 position:33% line:83% align:start
I need to get
all the way to the bench.

00:12:11.031 --> 00:12:12.199 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:12:12.233 --> 00:12:13.400 position:33% line:89% align:start
Of course...

00:12:13.434 --> 00:12:14.703 position:35% line:89% align:start
[grunting]

00:12:14.735 --> 00:12:16.103 position:24% line:89% align:start
Oh, my dear Misugi.

00:12:16.136 --> 00:12:19.373 position:35% line:83% align:start
Oh darling,
we should be proud of him.

00:12:19.406 --> 00:12:21.208 position:13% line:89% align:start
Jun is an excellent player.

00:12:21.242 --> 00:12:22.943 position:35% line:89% align:start
Yes, he is.

00:12:24.778 --> 00:12:25.680 position:44% line:83% align:start
[Jun]
Tsubasa Ozora.

00:12:25.714 --> 00:12:26.880 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:12:26.914 --> 00:12:29.450 position:16% line:83% align:start
I decided I won't give up
on soccer just yet.

00:12:31.118 --> 00:12:31.519 position:44% line:89% align:start
Mhm.

00:12:32.786 --> 00:12:35.756 position:19% line:83% align:start
Even if I can only play
two minutes next time...

00:12:35.789 --> 00:12:38.526 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'll step on the pitch
one more time for sure.

00:12:38.560 --> 00:12:39.760 position:30% line:89% align:start
And some day...

00:12:39.793 --> 00:12:42.564 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'll completely recover
from my heart condition.

00:12:42.597 --> 00:12:44.298 position:27% line:89% align:start
I know you will.

00:12:44.331 --> 00:12:54.475 position:35% line:89% align:start
[cheering]

00:12:54.509 --> 00:12:55.744 position:41% line:83% align:start
[narr]
 <i>Team Nankatsu wins</i>

00:12:55.776 --> 00:12:59.947 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>by a 5-4 goal difference</i>
 <i>against Team Musashi.</i>

00:12:59.980 --> 00:13:03.017 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>We'll be right back</i>
 <i>with Captain Tsubasa.</i>

00:13:06.420 --> 00:13:07.555 position:41% line:83% align:start
[narr]
 <i>And we're back.</i>

00:13:12.826 --> 00:13:14.028 position:24% line:89% align:start
Excuse me, captain,

00:13:14.061 --> 00:13:15.730 position:21% line:83% align:start
today is the big day
isn't it?

00:13:15.764 --> 00:13:17.632 position:33% line:83% align:start
The finals of
the national tournament.

00:13:17.666 --> 00:13:19.166 position:19% line:89% align:start
Yeah. It's a pity that

00:13:19.199 --> 00:13:21.902 position:19% line:83% align:start
I couldn't be in Japan
to see it.

00:13:21.935 --> 00:13:24.004 position:19% line:83% align:start
You don't have to worry
about that, Captain.

00:13:24.038 --> 00:13:25.272 position:21% line:83% align:start
You can see the match
from here

00:13:25.306 --> 00:13:27.074 position:21% line:89% align:start
and cheer on Tsubasa.

00:13:27.107 --> 00:13:29.443 position:13% line:83% align:start
We'll take care of the ship
meanwhile.

00:13:29.476 --> 00:13:31.278 position:38% line:83% align:start
Somehow,
that doesn't feel right.

00:13:31.312 --> 00:13:32.346 position:21% line:89% align:start
And why's that, sir?

00:13:33.180 --> 00:13:35.282 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>I wish you good luck,</i>
 <i>my son.</i>

00:13:41.756 --> 00:13:43.157 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Awww!
-[groaning]

00:13:43.190 --> 00:13:45.192 position:35% line:83% align:start
He's taking
way too long.

00:13:45.225 --> 00:13:49.463 position:19% line:83% align:start
Ugh, I wonder why he's
taking such a long time.

00:13:49.496 --> 00:13:50.565 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:13:50.598 --> 00:13:53.467 position:33% line:83% align:start
-Look, guys!
-[honking]

00:13:53.500 --> 00:13:54.536 position:38% line:89% align:start
He came!

00:13:54.569 --> 00:13:55.302 position:27% line:89% align:start
It's about time.

00:13:56.036 --> 00:13:58.305 position:41% line:83% align:start
[narr]
 <i>You go, Nankatsu!</i>

00:13:58.339 --> 00:13:59.873 position:27% line:89% align:start
It's incredible.

00:14:03.511 --> 00:14:05.714 position:19% line:89% align:start
Sorry about being late.

00:14:05.747 --> 00:14:07.181 position:21% line:89% align:start
You can come in now.

00:14:08.683 --> 00:14:11.519 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Sanae] Sir, thank you for
taking the time to take us.

00:14:11.553 --> 00:14:12.453 position:38% line:83% align:start
[driver]
It's no bother.

00:14:12.486 --> 00:14:14.756 position:35% line:83% align:start
Either way,
it's on the way to my job.

00:14:14.789 --> 00:14:16.290 position:27% line:83% align:start
Team Nankatsu is
very strong.

00:14:16.323 --> 00:14:18.192 position:24% line:83% align:start
And that's because
you guys cheer them on

00:14:18.225 --> 00:14:19.728 position:24% line:83% align:start
during the matches,
young miss.

00:14:19.761 --> 00:14:20.829 position:19% line:89% align:start
That's because we have

00:14:20.861 --> 00:14:22.396 position:19% line:83% align:start
our star player Tsubasa
with us, sir.

00:14:22.429 --> 00:14:25.032 position:13% line:83% align:start
While we're on the subject,
Tsubasa...

00:14:25.065 --> 00:14:26.133 position:21% line:83% align:start
He's your boyfriend,
right?

00:14:26.166 --> 00:14:27.736 position:44% line:83% align:start
What?
My boyfriend?

00:14:27.769 --> 00:14:28.770 position:33% line:83% align:start
Oh, come on.
What're you saying, sir?

00:14:28.803 --> 00:14:30.070 position:38% line:89% align:start
[scream]

00:14:30.104 --> 00:14:33.040 position:10% line:83% align:start
[driver] Hey, don't do that.
I'm driving, you know?

