00:15:52.352 --> 00:15:53.353 position:30% line:89% align:start
Right, Tsubasa?

00:15:54.254 --> 00:15:55.355 position:44% line:89% align:start
Yeah.

00:15:55.389 --> 00:15:56.390 position:24% line:89% align:start
Listen to me well.

00:15:57.157 --> 00:15:58.593 position:33% line:83% align:start
I want you to
give it your all

00:15:58.626 --> 00:15:59.627 position:19% line:89% align:start
