00:16:16.109 --> 00:16:18.780 position:19% line:83% align:start
 <i>to face off once more</i>
 <i>against Team Meiwa.</i>

00:16:18.813 --> 00:16:20.180 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>This is the moment</i>
 <i>of truth</i>

00:16:20.214 --> 00:16:21.516 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>we've been all</i>
 <i>waiting for.</i>

