Roberto and my mom.

00:17:25.178 --> 00:17:26.781 position:27% line:89% align:start
 <i>You did it, kid.</i>

00:17:26.814 --> 00:17:27.782 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>You're in the finals.</i>

00:17:29.017 --> 00:17:31.184 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa] <i>I'll keep</i>
 <i>my promise, Roberto.</i>

00:17:31.218 --> 00:17:33.253 position:16% line:83% align:start
 <i>I'll win and go with you</i>
 <i>to Brazil.</i>

