 <i>They haven't stepped</i>
 <i>onto the pitch.</i>

00:17:45.132 --> 00:17:46.466 position:38% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa]
 <i>They're running late.</i>

00:17:46.500 --> 00:17:47.502 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>What happened?</i>

00:17:50.905 --> 00:17:53.841 position:30% line:83% align:start
 <i>Could it be...</i>
 <i>that Hyuga's sick?</i>

00:17:53.875 --> 00:17:55.009 position:44% line:89% align:start
