 <i>Team Meiwa makes</i>
 <i>an appearance.</i>

00:18:08.056 --> 00:18:09.189 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Genzo]
 <i>You won't have it that easy</i>

00:18:09.222 --> 00:18:12.259 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>this time around,</i>
 <i>Kojiro Hyuga.</i>

00:18:12.292 --> 00:18:15.195 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Tsubasa] <i>Hyuga, I'm going</i>
 <i>to challenge you again.</i>

00:18:15.228 --> 00:18:18.700 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Takeshi] <i>Kojiro, we'll win</i>
 <i>the tournament finals.</i>

00:18:18.733 --> 00:18:19.634 position:38% line:89% align:start
 <i>Yeah...</i>

00:18:20.200 --> 00:18:21.201 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>After what he said,</i>

00:18:21.234 --> 00:18:23.470 position:24% line:83% align:start
 <i>we can't possibly</i>
 <i>be defeated.</i>

