win every match by myself.

00:19:18.826 --> 00:19:20.293 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Uh...
-Uh...

00:19:20.327 --> 00:19:22.697 position:16% line:83% align:start
In fact, had it not been
for you, Ken,

00:19:22.730 --> 00:19:25.365 position:24% line:83% align:start
