have my back.

00:19:32.439 --> 00:19:34.174 position:13% line:89% align:start
You're an exceptional team.

00:19:34.207 --> 00:19:36.577 position:19% line:83% align:start
A team that I can truly
count on.

00:19:36.611 --> 00:19:38.079 position:30% line:89% align:start
Captain Kojiro.

00:19:38.112 --> 00:19:40.014 position:27% line:83% align:start
I want us to play
this match together

00:19:40.048 --> 00:19:41.248 position:30% line:89% align:start
so we can win.

00:19:41.281 --> 00:19:42.684 position:30% line:83% align:start
Can I count on
every single one of you

00:19:42.717 --> 00:19:43.751 position:35% line:89% align:start
to do that?

