 <i>This is the first time</i>
 <i>that Kojiro recognizes us</i>

00:19:51.159 --> 00:19:52.126 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>as his teammates.</i>

00:19:52.160 --> 00:19:54.194 position:41% line:83% align:start
