And remember to bring
all of your water bottles.

00:20:35.268 --> 00:20:36.771 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Yeah!
-Yeah!

00:20:39.640 --> 00:20:41.743 position:27% line:83% align:start
 <i>I will give them</i>
 <i>a better life.</i>

00:20:43.044 --> 00:20:44.112 position:13% line:89% align:start
 <i>I will win this tournament</i>

00:20:44.145 --> 00:20:45.813 position:21% line:83% align:start
 <i>and we'll be crowned</i>
 <i>the champions.</i>

00:20:45.847 --> 00:20:47.380 position:16% line:89% align:start
 <i>Here we come, Nankatsu.</i>

00:20:49.183 --> 00:20:50.417 position:16% line:83% align:start
Who would've thought that
they would both

00:20:50.450 --> 00:20:52.186 position:19% line:89% align:start
