00:20:52.220 --> 00:20:53.320 position:41% line:89% align:start
Yes...

00:20:53.353 --> 00:20:55.489 position:13% line:83% align:start
However, this time will be
the last.

00:20:55.523 --> 00:20:57.892 position:27% line:83% align:start
Let's see who'll
come out on top.

00:21:02.663 --> 00:21:03.664 position:44% line:89% align:start
Okay.

00:21:03.698 --> 00:21:07.702 position:19% line:83% align:start
